    <item>
      <title>中国乐观的5%增长目标被视为“没有计划的目标”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-s-bullish-5-growth-goal-seen-as-target-without-a-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着高层领导人试图增强人们对世界第二大经济体的信心，中国设定了今年 5% 左右的增长目标。但对于一些分析人士来说，李强总理缺乏如何实现这一目标的细节，这与国家面临的严峻挑战格格不入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-s-bullish-5-growth-goal-seen-as-target-without-a-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储谨慎态度和中国经济增长担忧导致新兴市场下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/emerging-market-stocks-currencies-drop-on-china-growth-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，在香港上市的科技股带领新兴市场股市走低，此前宣布的旨在提振世界第二大经济体信心的措施令投资者感到失望。发展中国家货币涨跌互现，交易员等待重要讲话和数据，以阐明利率前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/emerging-market-stocks-currencies-drop-on-china-growth-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:01:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
