      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市波动，短暂抹去了盘中跌幅，交易员在评估好坏参半的美国经济数据，寻找利率走势的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/european-stocks-dip-after-fed-pushback-miners-lead-declines</guid>
